    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Only you and the gravity!</strong><br>Open-world maze that brings back the challenge of old-school retro games—no hints, no hand-holding.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306300/extras/ed6b2c4808f170b0e4dfd64a16d2cefa.poster.avif?t=1731658073\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306300/extras/ed6b2c4808f170b0e4dfd64a16d2cefa.webm?t=1731658073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306300/extras/ed6b2c4808f170b0e4dfd64a16d2cefa.mp4?t=1731658073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Key Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Open-world labyrinth</strong>: Explore at your own pace with no set paths or linear objectives.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unique puzzle mechanics</strong>: Solve puzzles by manipulating gravity in creative ways.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Retro  '80s neon style</strong>: A vibrant and nostalgic world inspired by classic video games.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>No hints, no help</strong>: You're on your own to solve every challenge and unlock the mysteries of the maze.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Top-down perspective</strong>: A classic viewpoint that adds to the retro feel.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Classic Real-time sound generation</strong>: Some audio effects are dynamically created by your computer.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Active leaderboard</strong>: Compete for the fastest playthrough times and show off your skills.</p></li></ul>",
